C-c C-h            insert header
C-u 11 C-n        move to line after header
C-o              insert newline

M-x w-cl               whitespace cleanup

C-u 5 C-n        move to first line containing declarations
C-u 3 C-K        kill lines with declaration
C-u 2 C-p        move to top of function
C-y                yank lines at top of function

M-f    <SPC>        move forward over `while`; insert space

C-u 11 C-n        move to line with break statement
M-f <SPC>        move forward over `break`; insert space

C-x h            select everything in buffer
C-M-\            indent selected region